column5: wish me luck after checking tomorrows weather and seeing there will be a ne to east wind Myself and fishindevil will be towing my boat over to pefferlaw or area and see if we can get into some perch or crappies, gonna feel good being in the boat again
Good fishin' Ernie...one more week and we can fish in our own backyards...
Best of luck guys...weather sounds good!  Have fun
That's what Shawn needs the wind blowing through his hair LOL good luck tomorrow  Rob
